cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on image recognition, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves deep learning and multi-task learning, which are also common in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions consistency-based methods, which are often used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG and cs.AI. The other two sub-categories are less likely but still possible based on the mentioned methods.
